s?\r\n\r\n<strong>Answer:</strong> We cannot guarantee the removal of 100% of all spots and stains because there are substances that permanently discolor the carpet. The age of the carpet and other factors come into play here, but we try to remove all spots and stains.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Question:</strong> There are bubbles and ripples in my carpet after it was cleaned. Is this normal?\r\n\r\n<strong>Answer:</strong> The bubbles and ripples should flatten on their own within a few days; however this is a sign that the carpet should have been stretched prior to cleaning. Please contact us as soon as possible if the the bubbles or ripples don''t go away: (989) 339-4205\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Question:</strong> Will carpet cleaning get rid of pests like fleas?\r\n\r\n<strong>Answer:</strong> We encourage you to kill all adult fleas and pests before carpet cleaning. A professional exterminator may be of more assistance in this matter. Fleas and other pests may lay eggs in other areas as well, so you may consider having all upholstery, area rugs, and pet beds treated and cleaned\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a class="button" href="/quote">Click for a Free Fast Quote</a>', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-07 13:45:21', '2016-12-07 18:45:21', '', 95, 'http://muddybootscarpetcleaning.com/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
